| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1109 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ff80f1f9-e55f-5f54-b17d-8e58658ae602"
